07 <a href=\"\/?p=4873\">negatywne s\u0142owa kluczowe<\/a> w odpowiedzi na sezonowe zmiany lub nowe trendy.<\/p>\n<li><b>\u015aled\u017a trendy.<\/b><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Wprowadzenie negatywnego targetowania do reklam displayowych to krok w stron\u0119 wi\u0119kszej skuteczno\u015bci i lepszego zarz\u0105dzania bud\u017cetem. Pami\u0119taj, aby regularnie analizowa\u0107 wyniki i dostosowywa\u0107 swoj\u0105 strategi\u0119.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><b>Jak skutecznie wykorzysta\u0107 negatywne targetowanie w reklamach na Amazonie?<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Czy wiesz, \u017ce dod<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3965,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3964","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3964"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3964"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3964\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3965"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3964"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3964"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3964"}],"curies"